Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.50,0:03:51.96,soryo soryo EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1}即使稱為悲哀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.00,0:03:54.88,soryo soryo EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1}希望 思い 信じつづけた
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.00,0:03:54.88,soryo soryo EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1}我也繼續相信這份希望和思念
